由他人演唱的歌曲根据自己的风格重新演唱，包括重新填词，编曲。现在已有不少明星，都在翻唱他人的歌，不断在翻唱中突破自己，给大家带来不一样的风格。视频示例： 有一种悲伤（翻唱）-《A Kind of Sorrow》</p>\n```\n\n:::\n\n### 文本格式化\n\n| 标签 | 说明   |\n| ---- | ------ |\n| b    | 加粗   |\n| u    | 下划线 |\n| i    | 倾斜   |\n| s    | 删除线 |\n\n::: warning\n强调语境下使用下列标签\n\n:::\n\n| 标签   | 说明   |\n| ------ | ------ |\n| strong | 加粗   |\n| ins    | 下划线 |\n| em     | 倾斜   |\n| del    | 删除线 |\n\n### 路径\n\n::: code-tabs\n@tab 绝对路径\n\n```text\n具体地址，如`C:\\Program Files\\7-Zip\\7-Zip.exe`\n```\n@tab 相对路径\n```bash\n./   //本级目录\n../  //上级目录\n~/   //根目录\n```\n:::\n\n### 媒体\n\n#### 图片\n::: info Emmet 语法\n`img`\n:::\n\n::: normal-demo\n\n```html\n<img src=\"/html/dog.gif\" alt=\"\">\n```\n\n:::\n\n`alt`：方便视觉障碍者或图片无法加载\n\n#### 视频\n::: info Emmet 语法\n`video`\n:::\n\n```html\n<video src=\"\"></video>\n```\n`controls`：显示控制条\n\n`loop`：循环\n\n#### 音频\n::: info Emmet 语法\n`audio`\n:::\n\n```html\n<audio src=\"\"><audio>\n```\n#### 链接\n::: info Emmet 语法\n`a`\n:::\n\n```html\n<a href=\"\" target=\"_self\"></a>\n<a href=\"\" target=\"_blank\"></a>  //新窗口\n```","excerpt":"","tasklists":0,"title":"","headers":[{"level":2,"title":"WEB标准","slug":"web标准","link":"#web标准","children":[]},{"level":2,"title":"骨架结构","slug":"骨架结构","link":"#骨架结构","children":[{"level":3,"title":"文档标识","slug":"文档标识","link":"#文档标识","children":[]},{"level":3,"title":"<html>","slug":"html","link":"#html","children":[]},{"level":3,"title":"<head>","slug":"head","link":"#head","children":[]},{"level":3,"title":"<body>","slug":"body","link":"#body","children":[]}]},{"level":2,"title":"常用标签","slug":"常用标签","link":"#常用标签","children":[{"level":3,"title":"标题","slug":"标题","link":"#标题","children":[]},{"level":3,"title":"换行和水平线标签","slug":"换行和水平线标签","link":"#换行和水平线标签","children":[]},{"level":3,"title":"段落标签","slug":"段落标签","link":"#段落标签","children":[]},{"level":3,"title":"文本格式化","slug":"文本格式化","link":"#文本格式化","children":[]},{"level":3,"title":"路径","slug":"路径","link":"#路径","children":[]},{"level":3,"title":"媒体","slug":"媒体","link":"#媒体","childre